room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by Amazing Escape Room Bloomfield in New York
room_description: Step on through the swingin’ doors and transport yerselves back to the late 1800’s. You and your cohorts have spent some time in the saloon having come up with a plan to get as much gold as you can carry outta that there bank next door. Pryin ears might have heard about a secret passage between the saloon and that locked up bank. Hiding yerselves away till the place closes, yall have just one hour till the owner comes back; get to quick thinkin how to get yer hands on that gold next door while avoiding those traps set up to stop yall.
